  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city sprawling along the coast at dusk. The sky is ablaze with vibrant colors, transitioning from a fiery orange and red near the horizon to softer pinks and purples higher up. Wispy clouds stretch across the sky, enhancing the dramatic effect. Below, the city is a sea of twinkling lights, suggesting a bustling urban center. A body of water, likely a bay, separates the city from a distant shoreline, and a long bridge extends across the water, connecting different parts of the urban landscape. The foreground features glimpses of trees and vegetation, indicating a higher vantage point.",
